# Flutter UI

- Reuse `lib/shared/widgets/` before creating widgets.
- Colors and shapes from `Theme.of(context)` and `AppTheme` — no magic literals.
- Fill available space; avoid shrinking primary content with nested frames.
- Extract when `build()` exceeds ~80 lines.

Load `.cursor/skills/flutter/ui/SKILL.md` for structure; load `.cursor/skills/project/ui-interactions/SKILL.md` for motion and tactile contract.
